text = "[b]Help[/b]\n- 1..6 choose offense.\n- Q/W/E/R choose defense in Hot Seat.\n- First downs use line-to-gain markers; penalties replay and can award first by yardage.\n- TD = 7, FG = 3 (range by distance, out-of-range is disallowed).\n- Punts can result in touchback to the 20.\n- Fumbles 50% recovery.\n- H toggles this overlay.\n- Quick Play: Enter. HUD: F1."

